| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1210 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5bfa87f3-790e-5cf3-889b-7e01736c1fd6"
